OL,5,
OL,6,CG1964FThe first edition of Play School
OL,7,Fairs on BBC Two. Due to a power failure
OL,8,Fthe previous evening (which should've
OL,9,Fbeen BBC Two launch night), Play School
OL,10,Fbecame the first scheduled programme to
OL,11,Fbe broadcast on BBC Two. A number of
OL,12,Funscheduled news bulletins were
OL,13,Fbroadcast on the channel on 20th April
OL,14,F1964.
OL,15,
OL,16,CG1964FThe first edition of Line-Up
OL,17,Fairs on BBC Two. The launch night
OL,18,Fedition of the programme (on 20th April
OL,19,F1964) was cancelled due to a power
OL,20,Ffailure.
