OL,6,CG2009FThe final edition of Alan
OL,7,FWhicker's Journey of a Lifetime airs on
OL,8,FBBC Two.
OL,9,
OL,10,FA four-part series in which veteran
OL,11,Fbroadcaster Alan Whicker sets off on a
OL,12,Fworld trip during which he reflects on
OL,13,Fhis life and career, beginning in
OL,14,FVenice, where he retraces his steps
OL,15,Ffrom soldier to journalist and thence
OL,16,Fto the world of television.
